**Starting Ability** | Ability Category
__Basics__
Starting Abilities are abilities that are automatically used when the player gains the role.
__Details__
Abilities that are automatically used when the player gains the role are considered to be starting abilities. Players gain roles at the start of the game and when a role change occurs. The bloody butcher disguises themself as a butcher as a Starting Ability. The Devil loses their soul as a Starting Ability.
